{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I came on-- I was supposed to anchor the ship within 50 yards of the designated geographic position.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, that's not particularly hard if you've got good visibility and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got up there, and I came in, and I took a visual fix.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if you know about taking a fix.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took a fix.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had the two tangents on the island-- boom, boom, here, and here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I cut it down the middle with a cupola on a-- on a little administrative building in the-- in the town of Garapan right over there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is at Saipan?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Saipan, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so the next morning, I went on the deck to see daylight to check my fix to see I hadn't moved overnight.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was anchored, you see?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got it-- but, goddammit, I couldn't find that town of Garapan-- gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What had happened was-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] the Army had-- you've got visitors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't find the town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What had happened was they had dropped leaflets over the entire island saying that every civilian target would be spared if they didn't use it for military purposes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in the middle of night, the Marines call out-- I mean, radioed out-- saying the Japs are forming up a counterattack in the town of Garapan.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, the entire US Navy opened up on Garapan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And friend, come daylight, there wasn't any Garapan left at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I later walked through it, and there was nothing but rubble-- heaps of rubble, a wasteland, nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything-- so anyway, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] this some-- well, they started shooting at me from sight from Tinian, which was down about three miles to my right.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
